{{other uses}}

The '''Fosi''' were a [[Germanic peoples|Germanic tribe]]. [[Tacitus]], in his ''[[Germania (Tacitus)|Germania]]'' mentions them as being neighbours of the [[Cherusci]], who suffered alongside Cherusci in their downfall. He also noted that before their mutual downfall, the Fosi were less prosperous than the Cherusci.{{sfn|Tacitus ''Ger.'' 36}}
