{{multiple image | direction = horizontal | align = right | footer = | image1 = Alexey Ivashchenko 1.jpg | caption1 = Aleksei Ivaschenko | width1 = 150 | image2 = G.Vasilyev 2017.jpg | caption2 = Georgy Vasilyev | width2 = 168 }} '''Aleksei Igorevich Ivaschenko''' ({{lang-ru|Алексей Игоревич Иващенко}}, born May 12, 1958 in [[Moscow]]) and '''Georgy Leonardovich Vasilyev''' ({{lang-ru|Георгий Леонардович Васильев}}, born June 22, 1957 in [[Zaporizhia]], [[Ukraine]]) are a Soviet/Russian [[Bard (Soviet Union)|bard]] duo, informally known as '''Ivasi'''. They have also written and staged the musical ''[[Nord-Ost]]''.
