{{Infobox Airport | name = Kasane International Airport | nativename = | nativename-a = | nativename-r = | image = Kasane Airport.jpg | image-width = 200 | IATA = BBK | ICAO = FBKE | pushpin_map = Botswana | pushpin_map_caption = Location of the airport in Botswana | pushpin_label = '''BBK''' | pushpin_label_position = right | FAA = | type = Public | owner = | operator = Botswana Department of Civil Aviation | city-served = [[Kasane]], [[Botswana]] | location = | elevation-f = 3290 | elevation-m = | coordinates = {{Coord|17|49|55|S|25|09|50|E|type:airport}} | website = | metric-elev = | metric-rwy = y | r1-number = 8/26 | r1-length-f = | r1-length-m = 3000 | r1-surface = Asphalt | stat-year = | stat1-header = | stat1-data = | stat2-header = | stat2-data = | footnotes = Sources: GCM<ref>{{GCM|BBK|Kasane Airport}}</ref> Google Maps<ref>[https://www.google.com/maps/@-17.8304104,25.1670975,5675m/data=!3m1!1e3 Google Maps - Kasane]</ref> }}
'''Kasane International Airport''' {{airport codes|BBK|FBKE}} is an airport serving [[Kasane]], a town in the [[North-West District (Botswana)|North-West District]] of [[Botswana]]. The airport is along the A33 Road, {{convert|4|km}} south of the town and {{convert|4|km}} south of the border with [[Namibia]].
[[Air Botswana]] provides scheduled service between [[Kasane]] and [[Gaborone]] on Tuesdays, Fridays, and Sundays. Numerous charter flight operators offer flights to other destinations in the vicinity.
Because it is near [[Chobe National Park]], the airport is mainly used for tourism.{{fact|date=June 2013}} Most lodges in the Kasane area provide shuttles from and to the airport. A bus shuttle is available for travel to [[Victoria Falls]] in [[Zimbabwe]].
==Airlines and destinations== {{Airport-dest-list |[[Air Botswana]]|[[Sir Seretse Khama International Airport|Gaborone]], [[OR Tambo International Airport|Johannesburg–OR Tambo]], [[Maun Airport|Maun]] |[[Airlink]]|[[OR Tambo International Airport|Johannesburg–OR Tambo]] }}
==Charter operators== *[[Wilderness Air]] - [[Eros Airport|Windhoek]] to Kasane.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.wilderness-air.com/where-we-are/botswana/|title=Wilderness Air » Botswana|website=www.wilderness-air.com|language=en-US|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref> * [[Moremi Air Services]]
