'''Orienbank''' is one of the oldest banks in [[Tajikistan]], and one of its largest financial institutions.<ref>{{cite news |title=Tajikistan: A Ruling Family Feud Appears to Turn Bloody |url=http://www.eurasianet.org/departments/insight/articles/eav050908a.shtml |work=EurasiaNet |publisher=[[Open Society Institute]] |date=8 May 2008 |accessdate=2 July 2012 }}</ref> The bank is currently led by chairman Hasan Asadullozoda.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nbt.tj/en/banking_system/list-of-the-credit-organizations.php |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2016-05-09 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160512171341/http://nbt.tj/en/banking_system/list-of-the-credit-organizations.php |archivedate=2016-05-12 |df= }}</ref>

