{{Infobox diocese | jurisdiction = Diocese<!-- Type of jurisdiction: i.e. Diocese or Archdiocese --> | name = Incheon | latin = Dioecesis Inchonensis | local = 인천 교구 | image = Dapdong cathedral 2.JPG | image_size = 200px | image_alt = | caption = Cathedral of St. Paul <!---- Locations ----> | country = {{flag|South Korea}} | metropolitan = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Seoul|Seoul]] | territory = | province = [[Roman Catholic Archdiocese of Seoul|Seoul]] | coordinates = <!-- Use {{coord}} --> <!---- Statistics ----> | area_km2 = 1,282<!-- Area in square kilometers, automatically converted --> | population = 4,240,000 | population_as_of = 2006 | catholics = 397,256<!-- Number of Catholics in the diocese --> | catholics_percent = 9.4 | parishes = 102<!-- Number of parishes in the diocese --> | churches = <!-- Number of churches in the diocese --> | congregations = <!-- Number of congregations in the diocese --> | schools = <!-- Number of church supported schools in the diocese --> | members = <!-- Number of members in the diocese --> <!---- Information ----> | denomination = [[Catholic Church]] | rite = [[Roman Rite]] | established = 6 June 1961 ({{age|1961|6|6}} years ago) | cathedral = Cathedral of St Paul in [[Incheon]] | cocathedral = | patron = | priests = <!-- Number of priests in the diocese --> <!---- Current leadership ----> | pope = {{Incumbent pope}} | bishop = [[John Baptist Jung Shin-chul]] | bishop_title = Bishop | coadjutor = | metro_archbishop = [[Andrew Yeom Soo-jung]] | auxiliary_bishops = Vacant | vicar_general = | emeritus_bishops = [[William John McNaughton]] <small>Bishop Emeritus (1962-2002)</small> <!---- Map ----> | map = Diocese of Incheon.svg | map_alt = | map_caption = <!---- Website ----> | website = [http://www.caincheon.or.kr/ Website of the Diocese] | footnotes = }} The '''Roman Catholic Diocese of Incheon''' ({{lang-la|Dioecesis Inchonensis}}) is a [[diocese]] of the [[Latin Rite]] of the [[Catholic Church]] located in [[Incheon]], [[South Korea]]. The diocese is [[suffragan]] to the [[Archdiocese of Seoul]].
==History== On 6 June 1961 [[Pope John XXIII]] erected as an [[Apostolic Vicariate]] of Incheon. It was elevated to a [[diocese]] the next year on 10 March. The seat is [[Dapdong Cathedral]].<ref name=hierarchy>{{cite web|url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dinch.html|title=Diocese of Incheon|publisher=Catholic-Hierarchy|accessdate=2014-02-12}}</ref><ref name=GCatholic>{{cite web|url=http://www.gcatholic.org/dioceses/diocese/inch0.htm|title=Diocese of Incheon|publisher=Giga Catholic|accessdate=2014-02-12}}</ref>
