{{unref|date=July 2017}}
'''Télévision Malagasy''' (TVM) is the national broadcaster of Madagascar. Established in 1965. To achieve national dissemination of programmes across Madagascar, the channels broadcast on the EutelSat satellite at 16 ° East. Likewise it is also used for the diffusion of Radio Madagascar said on the radio FM  at 99.00Mhz.

